description: Per-domain Pydantic API schemas (backend)
globs: backend/**/schemas.py
alwaysApply: false
---

# Backend — Pydantic (`schemas.py`)

- Request/response schemas colocated with the domain (`ChatRequest`, `*Response`, `*Item`, etc.) — follow neighboring domains.
- Fields aligned with SQLAlchemy models and the actual JSON API; keep names consistent with `routes.py` endpoints.
- Validation via types and `Field`; reuse existing enums from `backend.models` when they already represent the same values.
